creator: Elizabeth Chase Akers Allen
description: LibriVox volunteers bring you 17 recordings of Rock Me to Sleep by Elizabeth Chase Akers Allen. This was the Fortnightly Poetry project for January 18, 2015. Read in English by Adele de Pignerolles; Ardallion; elliot; DomBombadil; David Lawrence; Ezwa; fshort; Greg Giordano; Gemma L Myers; Jannie Meisberger; kgon; Larry Wilson; Leonard Wilson; MaryAnn; SteveToner; TriciaG and Vanessa Garcia. Elizabeth Chase Akers Allen was an American author, journalist and poet. (Summary from Wikipedia) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
